1.  be able to compare time elapsed between different algorithms and different implementations of the same algorithm
2.  be able to accept delimited list of text and salt combinations
3.  have GUI version AND command line version
4.  Be able to create an appendable merkle tree.  Act as client to verify that text provided is in merkle tree.
5.  Be able to store merkle tree
6.  Be able to store statistics about other hash operations (#1-3)
7.  While we are on crazy requirements, how about graphic visualizations about how various hash functions work?
    User can enter text of their choosing and watch the algorithm go to work on their text!
